metadata.name: Meme Mint Medallion #2
metadata.description: The Meme Mint Medallions are of the most coveted objects created by The Meme Mint. In addition to its grandiose splendor, the medallion offers its owner exclusive perks including an NFT drop from every collection produced by The Meme Mint on release and increased political weight in the community. Only five will ever be minted.
